%table.lookup
  - @radicals.each_slice(4) do |row|
    %tr
      - row.each do |radical|
        %td.chinese-lookup
          = link_to radical.simplified, first_radical_lookup_path(radical)
%p  
  Do you recognize any of the radicals above in the character which you are trying to identify? E.g. if you're looking for 
  %span.chinese 脑 
  then click on 
  = succeed '.' do
    %span.chinese 月

- if Rails.env == "production" && !(user_signed_in? && current_user.class.name == "Admin")
  :javascript
    mixpanel.track("Lookup");